text: Vladimír Frák (born 15 August 1961) is a Slovak skier. He competed in the Nordic combined event at the 1984 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1961 births Category:Living people Category:Slovak male Nordic combined skiers Category:Olympic Nordic combined skiers of Czechoslovakia Category:Nordic combined skiers at the 1984 Winter Olympics Category:People from Levoča
